---
// Contact CTA section for work detail page
---

<div class="px-6 md:px-12 py-12 md:py-16">
  <div class="max-w-[700px] mx-auto">
    <div
      class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-5 md:gap-8 p-6 md:p-8 bg-noto-bg-alt rounded-xl text-center md:text-left"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
        <span
          class="text-[0.6875rem] font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-noto-text-muted"
        >
          Contact
        </span>
        <p class="text-[0.9375rem] text-noto-text">
          お仕事のご相談はお気軽にどうぞ
        </p>
      </div>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3.5 bg-noto-accent text-white text-[0.8125rem] font-medium rounded-md transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-[#2e4660] shrink-0"
      >
        お問い合わせ
        <svg
          width="14"
          height="14"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
        >
          <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
